
Overview of noun mania

The noun mania has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (2) mania, passion, cacoethes -- (an irrational but irresistible motive for a belief or action)
2. mania, manic disorder -- (a mood disorder; an affective disorder in which the victim tends to respond excessively and sometimes violently)
